$ kubectl taint node node-name key=value:effect

effect types:- NoSchedule - PreferNoSchedule - NoExecute

ex:
$ kubectl taint node node01 color=blue:NoSchedule

when we want to add a pod to the node with taint color=blue:NoSchedule

pod-def.yml:
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: myapp-pod
    labels:
      app: myapp
      type: front-end
spec:
  containers:
    - name: nginx-container
      image: nginx
  toleration:
   - key: "color"
     value: "blue"
     operator: "Equal"
     effect: "NoSchedule"
